[1854.376981, "o", "\u001b[12;1H\u001b[13;1H\u001b[7m-----Info: (grep)Invoking, 22 lines --10%-----------------------------------\u001b[0m\u001b[1;1H\u001b[K\u001b[2;1H2 Invoking ‘grep’\u001b[3;1H*****************\u001b[4;1H\u001b[K\u001b[5;1HThe general synopsis of the ‘grep’ command line is\u001b[6;1H\u001b[K\u001b[7;1H     grep [OPTION...] [PATTERNS] [FILE...]\u001b[8;1H\u001b[K\u001b[9;1HThere can be zero or more OPTION arguments, and zero or more FILE\u001b[10;1Harguments.  The PATTERNS argument contains one or more patterns\u001b[K\u001b[11;1Hseparated by newlines, and is omitted when patterns are given via the\u001b[12;1H‘-e PATTERNS’ or ‘-f FILE’ options.  Typically PATTERNS should be quoted\u001b[12;1H"]
[1854.377028, "o", "\u001b[12;1H"]
[1854.408977, "o", "\u001b[12;1H\u001b[13;1H\u001b[7m-----Info: (grep)Invoking, 22 lines --20%-----------------------------------\u001b[0m\u001b[1;1H2 Invoking ‘grep’\u001b[2;1H*****************\u001b[3;1H\u001b[K\u001b[4;1HThe general synopsis of the ‘grep’ command line is\u001b[5;1H\u001b[K\u001b[6;1H     grep [OPTION...] [PATTERNS] [FILE...]\u001b[7;1H\u001b[K\u001b[8;1HThere can be zero or more OPTION arguments, and zero or more FILE\u001b[9;1Harguments.  The PATTERNS argument contains one or more patterns\u001b[K\u001b[10;1Hseparated by newlines, and is omitted when patterns are given via the\u001b[11;1H‘-e PATTERNS’ or ‘-f FILE’ options.  Typically PATTERNS should be quoted\u001b[12;1Hwhen ‘grep’ is used in a shell command.\u001b[K\u001b[12;1H"]
[1854.409067, "o", "\u001b[12;1H"]
