[1854.536225, "o", "\u001b[8;1Hwhen ‘grep’ is used in a shell command.\u001b[K\u001b[9;1H\u001b[K\u001b[10;1H* Menu:\u001b[11;1H\u001b[K\u001b[12;1H\u001b[1m* Command-line Options\u001b[0m::        Short and long names, grouped by category.\u001b[K\u001b[12;1H"]
