[1854.59934, "o", "\u001b[6;1Hwhen ‘grep’ is used in a shell command.\u001b[K\u001b[7;1H\u001b[K\u001b[8;1H* Menu:\u001b[9;1H\u001b[K\u001b[10;1H\u001b[4m* Command-line Options\u001b[24m::        Short and long names, grouped by category.\u001b[K\u001b[11;1H\u001b[4m* Environment Variables\u001b[24m::       POSIX, GNU generic, and GNU grep specific.\u001b[K\u001b[12;1H\u001b[1m* Exit Status\u001b[0m::                 Exit status returned by ‘grep’.\u001b[K\u001b[12;1H"]
