[1855.485457, "o", "\u001b[13;1H\u001b[7m-----Info: (grep)Generic Program Information, 14 lines --Top----------------\u001b[0m\u001b[1;1HNext: Matching Control,  Up: Command-line Options\u001b[2;1H\u001b[K\u001b[3;1H\u001b[K\u001b[3;1H2.1.1 Generic Program Information\u001b[4;1H\u001b[K\u001b[4;1H---------------------------------\u001b[5;1H\u001b[K\u001b[6;1H\u001b[K\u001b[6;1H‘--help’\u001b[7;1H\u001b[K\u001b[7;1H     Print a usage message briefly summarizing the command-line options\u001b[8;1H\u001b[K\u001b[8;1H     and the bug-reporting address, then exit.\u001b[10;1H‘-V’\u001b[K\u001b[11;1H\u001b[K\u001b[11;1H‘--version’\u001b[12;1H     Print the version number of ‘grep’ to the standard output stream.\u001b[1;1H"]
