[1855.868278, "o", "\u001b[12;1H\u001b[13;1H\u001b[7m-----Info: (grep)Generic Program Information, 14 lines --50%----------------\u001b[0m\u001b[1;1H\u001b[K\u001b[2;1H2.1.1 Generic Program Information\u001b[3;1H---------------------------------\u001b[4;1H\u001b[K\u001b[5;1H‘--help’\u001b[6;1H     Print a usage message briefly summarizing the command-line options\u001b[7;6Hand the bug-reporting address, then exit.\u001b[K\u001b[8;1H\u001b[K\u001b[9;1H‘-V’\u001b[10;3H-version’\u001b[11;1H     Print the version number of ‘grep’ to the standard output stream.\u001b[12;6HThis version number should be included in all bug reports.\u001b[K\u001b[12;1H\u001b[12;1H"]
[1855.89892, "o", "\u001b[12;1H\u001b[13;1H\u001b[7m-----Info: (grep)Generic Program Information, 14 lines --Bot----------------\u001b[0m\u001b[1;1H2.1.1 Generic Program Information\u001b[2;1H---------------------------------\u001b[3;1H\u001b[K\u001b[4;1H‘--help’\u001b[5;1H     Print a usage message briefly summarizing the command-line options\u001b[6;6Hand the bug-reporting address, then exit.\u001b[K\u001b[7;1H\u001b[K\u001b[8;1H‘-V’\u001b[9;3H-version’\u001b[10;1H     Print the version number of ‘grep’ to the standard output stream.\u001b[11;6HThis version number should be included in all bug reports.\u001b[K\u001b[12;1H\u001b[K\u001b[12;1H"]
